Description: COSMIC desktop panel applet for internet radio streaming
 A minimalist COSMIC panel applet for streaming internet radio stations.
 Features include station management via TOML config, now-playing metadata
 display, volume control, PLS playlist support, and album artwork caching.
 .
 This applet integrates natively with the COSMIC desktop environment.
